                      <span>2004-01-20</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book provides an another resource in addition to the PCI Express Specification. This is helpful since I'm at a small company where no one else is working on PCI Express at the moment. The book is well written and well organized. It is useful to me as a system architect as well as the other guys in my group who will be the designers on our next ASIC project.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">book review</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
